Hi <%= @login %>,

A maintainer of the @<%= @org.display_login%> organization has blocked you<%= @duration if @duration %> because of <%= @content_url.present? ? "this content: #{@content_url}" : "a recent post" %>.

<%
  message = [" For more information please see"]

  if @coc_url
    message << @coc_url
  else
    message << "#{GitHub.help_url}/articles/github-community-guidelines"
  end
  message << "contact the maintainer at #{@org.profile_email}" unless @org.profile_email.blank?

  message = message.to_sentence(two_words_connector: " or ", last_word_connector: ", or")
%>
<%= "#{message}." %>

Thanks,
The GitHub Team
